Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.72,0:00:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們因為不願被奪走情感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而發出的吶喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.33,0:00:10.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們並非為死亡而悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為不能活得像個正常人而傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.87,0:00:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.71,0:00:25.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘大本營 月亮二號
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒想到竟然是如此巨大的衛星殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快進入他們的防衛圈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.57,0:00:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想奪回吉歐可不是什麼輕而易舉的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶藏不都這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過能輕易到手的稀世寶貝？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.43,0:00:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 這話不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:52.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 等著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.98,0:00:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會救出你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.57,0:01:01.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星移民計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.21,0:01:05.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因其失敗被遺留在火星圈的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.44,0:01:08.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱獨立國家維甘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向地球聯邦政府宣戰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.96,0:01:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭開始 已將近70年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺說過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:11.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特是邪惡的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.14,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘必須被打倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 真的是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.98,0:03:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想認識更多人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.14,0:03:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去更多的地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活得更像個人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏她…到底做錯了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特大人有事想和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:47.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事希望你幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.77,0:03:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不為別的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是關於你的機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們製造的新型高達
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經離問世不遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.71,0:04:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駕駛員使用的認證裝置構造複雜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未能完全破解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.01,0:04:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能知道那位少年生物信息的認證代碼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.64,0:04:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想破解裝置幹什麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒有必要知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 我可以幫你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我有個條件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要藥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去給她 給露烏治病用！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣？給我藥的話我就幫你們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有藥物可以使那種病痊癒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.91,0:05:02.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量延緩病情發展 知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會吩咐人準備
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成認證
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,密碼程序數據也回收完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.14,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 伊澤爾坎特先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.85,0:06:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.46,0:06:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你不要再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐？是吉歐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.33,0:06:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.39,0:06:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 我該如何感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺已經好點了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.19,0:06:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會這麼快見效的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:44.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得就是這麼快！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.47,0:06:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的謝謝你 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼貴重的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哪兒搞到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.45,0:06:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了晚飯再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.81,0:07:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多坐會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.54,0:07:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那些話別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.87,0:07:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.01,0:07:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以後還會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏隨時歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見 露烏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這已經是第幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.76,0:07:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著那孩子的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.49,0:07:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像羅米還活著一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你畫得？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.11,0:08:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏有繪畫的才能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.34,0:08:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘！ 猜猜是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.75,0:08:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把吉歐來的事 寫在日記上了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.36,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.93,0:08:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還寫了一點 未來的日記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和吉歐一起散步
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在廢山上眺望景色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.88,0:09:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去不了外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想 如果能這樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.21,0:09:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想出去看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服用著吉歐的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出去稍微走走應該沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:30.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去去就回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.68,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.36,0:09:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 快來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 這是去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.46,0:10:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這附近我不太認識
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個好地方帶你去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.77,0:10:11.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記上寫的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.66,0:10:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生病以前經常去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:18.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是附近風景最漂亮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.47,0:10:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.40,0:10:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 這裏這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:38.15,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如小道綿延般
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:44.16,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}願此時光長存
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:50.90,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聽山丘上的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:56.88,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}訴說凄慘的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.99,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:09.12,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}令世界絢麗多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:15.66,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}讓離別再多等片刻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:21.41,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}盡情擁抱溫馨時光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:28.78,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}為你不再傷心落淚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:34.18,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}我努力獻上微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:40.89,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}明明能做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:47.16,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}卻被誠實的淚水揭穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:53.47,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}初識生的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.82,0:12:01.61,INCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}試著低聲說出「幸福…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這裏這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.32,0:12:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.72,0:12:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.32,0:12:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地球一定比這裏更美吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.29,0:12:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:42.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日記上寫的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.46,0:12:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來嘍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.95,0:13:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:10.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 露烏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.76,0:13:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.22,0:13:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去躺會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.31,0:13:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.53,0:13:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.63,0:13:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始 雖說不想讓你再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是想到 就算吃了藥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏剩下的時間也不會太長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 正因為這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才想讓她過得更開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.86,0:14:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不愧是維甘的隱身傘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的戰艦殘骸渾身是寶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到海盜大展身手的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:28.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我們要找的寶藏是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DarkHunter出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏出現敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 韋氏蒂安利用了隱形技術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄靠近過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.50,0:14:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他們竟然擁有我們的技術
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你對付他們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡可能避免損失
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:14:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 不許吉歐·明日野走出房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.79,0:15:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為奪回高達做好準備工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.36,0:15:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去營救吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.21,0:15:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 首先是找出吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.08,0:15:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.33,0:15:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-23區 嚴防官邸上空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.57,0:15:38.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝指示
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:15:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開門 開門啊！喂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.33,0:16:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.76,0:16:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是感動的重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:22.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少來湊熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.15,0:16:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了 沒有多餘的時間奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.04,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.10,0:16:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.56,0:16:48.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 你到底在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.34,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.07,0:17:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.84,0:17:08.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有話待會兒說 先上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.42,0:17:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去找高達
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:33.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在想什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會救你出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這座月亮二號
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是亞修船長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:47.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE-3那邊進展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.31,0:17:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.44,0:17:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經入侵格納庫管理系統
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時聽候吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK 動手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.75,0:17:56.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.51,0:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？開火！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:22.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.46,0:18:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.65,0:18:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.03,0:18:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早給你拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.58,0:18:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.79,0:18:37.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追！追！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.08,0:18:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 快
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:18:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事要去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:18:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須去給朋友送一樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不看這是什麼時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 回來 吉歐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏一定是幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:19:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.75,0:20:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要這麼說！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…什麼也沒為她…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該看看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.54,0:20:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏自從遇見你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:21.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了什麼是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 你原來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 來屏幕顯示的匯合地點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.20,0:20:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏把未來的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來的記憶 寫在日記上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括很遠的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.08,0:20:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天和吉歐一起去了公園
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕩鞦韆 蹺蹺板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:58.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩什麼都開心！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐今天感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次輪到我照顧吉歐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.05,0:21:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像吉歐做的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一直陪在他身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.22,0:21:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是吉歐的生日！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在生日卡上寫道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐在身邊 我就開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.75,0:21:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的病也一定會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.75,0:21:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐 突破大門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露烏…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.37,0:21:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 吉歐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.64,0:21:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.45,0:21:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吉歐在 世界也變得絢麗多姿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.11,0:21:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我 終於和吉歐來到了地球上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片和吉歐共同踏上的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始新的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉歐因得知敵人的真相而猶豫不決
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊澤爾坎特與吉歐的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.03,0:24:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在赤紅的宇宙中碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.14,0:24:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 機動戰士高達AGE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.54,0:24:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通向新世界的門扉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.56,0:24:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人的命運成就歷史
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.08,0:24:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星圈的殖民衛星中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.55,0:24:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最大的就是 維甘的根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮二號
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.57,0:24:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維甘的首領伊澤爾坎特就坐鎮這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向進攻地球的維甘部隊下達指示

